Installation
------------
In the php.ini file:
- make sure that always_populate_raw_post_data = On

Copy voxb.ini_INSTALL to voxb.ini and edit it to reflect your setup

Copy voxb.wsdl_INSTALL to voxb.wsdl and modify
the location of the service (at the end of the file)

